723690f-a.title: Manhattan: Van Corlear Place - 227th Street (West)
723690f-a.text:
Van Corlear Place, north from Jacobus Place to West 227th
Street, as photographed to show pavement conditions. These
photos are progressive. In the last appears a modern apart-
ment bldg. on the north side of 227th Street. The grade
there slopes down to Marble Hill Avente
May 3, 1937
1-2-3
W. P. A., photo
Five Boroughs Project
